item.title: CVE-2019-10440|2024-08-04T22:24:18.022Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20neoload%20plugin
item.description: Jenkins NeoLoad Plugin 2.2.5 and earlier stored credentials unencrypted in its global configuration file and in job config.xml files on the Jenkins master where they could be viewed by users with Extended Read permission, or access to the master file system.
